item.title: How do i make my self donater?
item.dc:creator: @Mitko Mitko
item.description:
@Mitko wrote:

You know how to make a donator shop but you can’t make yourself a donator?..
Go into your character file and look for “donator” if it’s 0 change to 1
Also, look in your cfg files you may have donators.txt if you have it, put your account name there.
